些尴尬的替代图来对底层分布进行建模，但替代图似乎并不比更直观的起始图更好。更一般地说，我们的重新扎根马尔可夫链的规则通常可用作较长推导的中间体；真正的价值并不在于将其用作独立规则。</p><h3>更一般的重新生根规则</h3><p>更一般地说，任何形式的图表</p><figure class="image"><img src="https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/XHtygebvHoJSSeNPP/mopix5jc2ebnvjoxey5b"><figcaption></figcaption></figure><p>等价于相同形式的任何其他图（即采用任何其他“根节点” <span><span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="i"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">i</span></span></span></span></span></span></span> ）。</p><p>对于近似，如果基础分布<i>近似</i>满足以下形式的任何图</p><figure class="image"><img src="https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/XHtygebvHoJSSeNPP/f30g0fxhaxrqdl0dae6p"><figcaption></figcaption></figure><p>到<span><span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="\epsilon"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.225em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">ϵ</span></span></span></span></span></span></span>内，那么它满足<span><span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="\epsilon"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.225em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">ϵ</span></span></span></span></span></span></span>内的所有其他条件。</p><p>再说一次，因为这是我们的第一条规则，所以让我们解开这个紧凑的符号。图表</p><figure class="image"><img src="https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/XHtygebvHoJSSeNPP/pwxenqmkixqde9sfhzow"><figcaption></figcaption></figure><p>表示因式分解</p><p><span><span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="P[X_1, …, X_n] = (\prod_{i \leq k} P[X_{i-1} | X_i]) P[X_k] (\prod_{k \leq i \leq n-1} P[X_{i+1} | X_i])"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"